PART VII.  RETIREMENT FOR CLASS C PUBLIC OFFICERS
AND EMPLOYEES

A.  Applicability of Part II
	    The following provisions of part II of this chapter shall apply to this part:



	(1)	Subpart A, except the definitions provided in section 88-21, unless expressly adopted in section 88-261;
	(2)	Subpart B, except sections 88-45, 88-46, 88-52, 88-59, 88-59.5, 88-59.6, 88-61, 88-62, and 88-45.5;
	(3)	Subpart C, except sections 88-71 to 88-76, 88-79, 88-80, 88-83, 88-84 to 88-85, 88-87 to 88-89, 88-96, 88-97, and 88-98;
	(4)	Subpart D, except sections 88-112 and 88-113; and
	(5)	Subpart E. [L 1984, c 108, pt of §8; am L 1987, c 117, §3; am L 1990, c 104, §3; am L 1998, c 151, §12; am L 2004, c 179, §23]
